node.title: Police investigate stabbing in Palmerston North
node.description: Police say a man with a serious stab wound was found on a footpath in Palmerston North early this morning.
node.content:
["Police say a man with a serious stab wound was found on a footpath in Palmerston North early this morning.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Patrice Allen\n
", "Police say they were called to Pinedale Parade in the suburb of Milson at about 2am and found the injured man.", "The man was taken to hospital and is undergoing surgery.", "Police say they do not believe it was a random attack and they are still making inquiries and examining the scene."]
